Read an HMMER3 formatted profile HMM

Source: R/io-methods.R
read_hmm.Rd

Read an HMMER3 formatted profile HMM

Usage

read_hmm(file)

Arguments

file

Path to a profile HMM generated with HMMER3

Value

A base::list().

Examples

read_hmm(padlocdev_example("protein.hmm"))
